lead_paragraph: Champions Bayern Munich must defeat Bayer Leverkusen on Saturday if they are to end an unusual losing run and avoid making a crisis out of what could be a brief dip in form.

headline.print_headline: From Predators to Prey, Bayern Must Turn Corner
